        "client_msg_id": "58c41e61-1c4f-447d-a7ec-837ea9f36b06",
        "text": "Also, the R components have a lot of words or expression that should not be translated included in the translation strings, where a placeholder like %s or (preferably) something more meaningful should be used.  For instance, `invalid nrows(z)` works be better of as `invalid %s`.",
